rows.label: qst200811_0010
rows.name:
Sorry to keep you waiting.
We'll make you all better.

rows.label: qst200811_0020
rows.name: How's it going? Is it working?

rows.label: qst200811_0030
rows.name:
Yes, it's okay. She should be
back to her old self in no time.

rows.label: qst200811_0040
rows.name:
That's great. I guess
our work here is done.

rows.label: qst200811_0060
rows.name:
Thank you! And I'm sure the tree would
thank you as well if she could!

rows.label: qst200811_0080
rows.name:
Even though it's just a
tree, I hope it knows that
everything is okay now.

rows.label: qst200811_0090
rows.name:
Of course she does! She's
just as aware as we are.

rows.label: qst200811_0100
rows.name:
What a world, eh? You learn
something every day.
